    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><br>Freddy Frog returns on his mission to be the highest frog in the world.<br>This frog just wants to keep jumping and you need to guide his hopping legs onto the next available platform.<br><br>Be careful. These platforms are not what they seem and a fall from a great height is not good for Freddy Frog.<br><br>Collect flies for extra points and avoid deadly wasps as you navigate treacherous procedurally generated platforms to get Freddy to the top of the high score table.<br><br>How high can you go?<br><br>This game is simple to understand but will test your platforming skills and ability to think fast.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br>Procedural platform and enemy generation will ensure no 2 play throughs are the same.<br>Simple game mechanics for quick pick up and play fun.<br>Stylized 3D model retro themed graphics.<br>Arcade style gameplay.<br>Online High Score Leaderboard.",
